Mr Pollard said he he would write to the Department of Health and Stockport NHS, University of South Manchester NHS Trust, where Mr Holland was also treated, over the concerns raised during the inquest.

He added that he would specifically ask for dentures to feature a metal marker on them so that they would show up on X-rays and scans.

